#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:5
msgid "Broad Crawls"
msgstr "广泛的爪子"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:7
msgid ""
"Scrapy defaults are optimized for crawling specific sites. These sites are "
"often handled by a single Scrapy spider, although this is not necessary or "
"required (for example, there are generic spiders that handle any given site "
"thrown at them)."
msgstr ""
"扫描默认值被优化用于覆盖特定站点。 这些场址往往由一个单一的废料喷洒器处理，但"
"没有必要或要求这样做（例如）。 那里有通用的喷雾器，处理任何向他们投掷的网"
"站)。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:12
msgid ""
"In addition to this \"focused crawl\", there is another common type of "
"crawling which covers a large (potentially unlimited) number of domains, and "
"is only limited by time or other arbitrary constraint, rather than stopping "
"when the domain was crawled to completion or when there are no more requests "
"to perform. These are called \"broad crawls\" and is the typical crawlers "
"employed by search engines."
msgstr ""
"除了这种“焦点角料”之外，还有另一种常见的覆盖大量（可能是无限制的）域。 而且只"
"受时间或其他任意限制， 而不是停止当域被夷为平地或没有更多的请求执行的时候。 "
"这些都叫做“大型箱子”，是搜索引擎使用的典型箱子。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:19
msgid "These are some common properties often found in broad crawls:"
msgstr "这些是一些常见的特性，常常出现在广泛的爪子里："

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:21
msgid ""
"they crawl many domains (often, unbounded) instead of a specific set of sites"
msgstr "他们捕捉了许多域名(常常是未弹出的) 而不是特定的站点。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:23
msgid ""
"they don't necessarily crawl domains to completion, because it would "
"impractical (or impossible) to do so, and instead limit the crawl by time or "
"number of pages crawled"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:27
msgid ""
"they are simpler in logic (as opposed to very complex spiders with many "
"extraction rules) because data is often post-processed in a separate stage"
msgstr ""
"它们在逻辑上比较简单(而不是具有许多提取规则的非常复杂的拼写器)，因为数据往往"
"是在一个单独的阶段后处理的。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:30
msgid ""
"they crawl many domains concurrently, which allows them to achieve faster "
"crawl speeds by not being limited by any particular site constraint (each "
"site is crawled slowly to respect politeness, but many sites are crawled in "
"parallel)"
msgstr ""
"它们同时捕捉许多域名， 允许他们通过不受任何特定站点约束的限制来实现更快的 "
"crawl 速度(每个站点都会慢慢地被压缩到尊重政治性的状态) 但许多站点平行被夷为平"
"地)"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:35
msgid ""
"As said above, Scrapy default settings are optimized for focused crawls, not "
"broad crawls. However, due to its asynchronous architecture, Scrapy is very "
"well suited for performing fast broad crawls. This page summarize some "
"things you need to keep in mind when using Scrapy for doing broad crawls, "
"along with concrete suggestions of Scrapy settings to tune in order to "
"achieve an efficient broad crawl."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:43
msgid "Increase concurrency"
msgstr "增加同义性"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:45
msgid ""
"Concurrency is the number of requests that are processed in parallel. There "
"is a global limit and a per-domain limit."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:48
msgid ""
"The default global concurrency limit in Scrapy is not suitable for crawling "
"many different  domains in parallel, so you will want to increase it. How "
"much to increase it will depend on how much CPU you crawler will have "
"available. A good starting point is ``100``, but the best way to find out is "
"by doing some trials and identifying at what concurrency your Scrapy process "
"gets CPU bounded. For optimum performance, You should pick a concurrency "
"where CPU usage is at 80-90%."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:56
msgid "To increase the global concurrency use::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:58
msgid "CONCURRENT_REQUESTS = 100"
msgstr "CONCRENT_REQUESTS = 100"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:61
msgid "Reduce log level"
msgstr "降低日志级别"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:63
msgid ""
"When doing broad crawls you are often only interested in the crawl rates you "
"get and any errors found. These stats are reported by Scrapy when using the "
"``INFO`` log level. In order to save CPU (and log storage requirements) you "
"should not use ``DEBUG`` log level when preforming large broad crawls in "
"production. Using ``DEBUG`` level when developing your (broad) crawler may "
"fine though."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:70
msgid "To set the log level use::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:72
msgid "LOG_LEVEL = 'INFO'"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:75
msgid "Disable cookies"
msgstr "禁用 cookie"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:77
msgid ""
"Disable cookies unless you *really* need. Cookies are often not needed when "
"doing broad crawls (search engine crawlers ignore them), and they improve "
"performance by saving some CPU cycles and reducing the memory footprint of "
"your Scrapy crawler."
msgstr ""
"禁用cookie，除非您*实际*需要。 在进行广泛的龙卷风时往往不需要cookie (搜索引擎"
"对它们置之不理)， 并通过保存一些CPU循环和减少废钢的内存足迹来提高性能。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:82
msgid "To disable cookies use::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:84
msgid "COOKIES_ENABLED = False"
msgstr "COOKIES_ENABLED = False"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:87
msgid "Disable retries"
msgstr "禁用重试"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:89
msgid ""
"Retrying failed HTTP requests can slow down the crawls substantially, "
"specially when sites causes are very slow (or fail) to respond, thus causing "
"a timeout error which gets retried many times, unnecessarily, preventing "
"crawler capacity to be reused for other domains."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:94
msgid "To disable retries use::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:96
msgid "RETRY_ENABLED = False"
msgstr "RETRY_ENABLED = False"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:99
msgid "Reduce download timeout"
msgstr "减少下载超时"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:101
msgid ""
"Unless you are crawling from a very slow connection (which shouldn't be the "
"case for broad crawls) reduce the download timeout so that stuck requests "
"are discarded quickly and free up capacity to process the next ones."
msgstr ""
"除非你从非常缓慢的连接中抓住(这种情况不应该是广泛的 crawls)，否则下载超时将会"
"减少，以便迅速丢弃被卡住的请求，并释放处理下一个请求的能力。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:105
msgid "To reduce the download timeout use::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:107
msgid "DOWNLOAD_TIMEOUT = 15"
msgstr "下载_TIMEOUT = 15"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:110
msgid "Disable redirects"
msgstr "禁用重定向"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:112
msgid ""
"Consider disabling redirects, unless you are interested in following them. "
"When doing broad crawls it's common to save redirects and resolve them when "
"revisiting the site at a later crawl. This also help to keep the number of "
"request constant per crawl batch, otherwise redirect loops may cause the "
"crawler to dedicate too many resources on any specific domain."
msgstr ""
"考虑禁用重定向，除非您有兴趣关注它们。 当执行广泛的板条箱时，通常是在稍后的板"
"条箱中重新定向和解析它们。 这也有助于保持每个crawl批量的请求数量不变， 否则，"
"重定向循环可能会导致爬行者将太多资源用于任何特定领域。"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:118
msgid "To disable redirects use::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:120
msgid "REDIRECT_ENABLED = False"
msgstr "REDIRECT_ENABLED = False"

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:123
msgid "Enable crawling of \"Ajax Crawlable Pages\""
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:125
msgid ""
"Some pages (up to 1%, based on empirical data from year 2013) declare "
"themselves as `ajax crawlable`_. This means they provide plain HTML version "
"of content that is usually available only via AJAX. Pages can indicate it in "
"two ways:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:130
msgid "by using ``#!`` in URL - this is the default way;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:131
msgid ""
"by using a special meta tag - this way is used on \"main\", \"index\" "
"website pages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:134
msgid ""
"Scrapy handles (1) automatically; to handle (2) enable :ref:"
"`AjaxCrawlMiddleware <ajaxcrawl-middleware>`::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:137
msgid "AJAXCRAWL_ENABLED = True"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/broad-crawls.rst:139
msgid ""
"When doing broad crawls it's common to crawl a lot of \"index\" web pages; "
"AjaxCrawlMiddleware helps to crawl them correctly. It is turned OFF by "
"default because it has some performance overhead, and enabling it for "
"focused crawls doesn't make much sense."
msgstr ""
